	<sect1 id="chap1sect1" label="1.1">
	<title>Minimum Requirements</title>
                <para>
                        Warning: This document is deprecated and refers to old code. 
                        A new document is being developed, but for now the best source 
                        of information can be found on 
                        <ulink url="https://sourceforge.net/docman/?group_id=4141">Sourceforge</ulink>.
                        This document may be wrong on a number of important issues, and it
                        will definitely waste your time.
                </para>
		<para>
			For purposes of this guide, requirements are very specific.  While 
			actual requirements may vary, this document's purpose is to guide 
			a user installing and configuring quickly.
		</para>
